OL,3,CPolice to use DNA tagging spray for
OL,4,Cthe first time at Sheffield derby
OL,6,FA DNA tagging spray will be used for
OL,7,Fthe first time at this weekend's
OL,8,FSheffield derby to identify people
OL,9,Finvolved in disorder.
OL,11,FSouth Yorkshire Police said it will be
OL,12,Fused by officers on the ground when
OL,13,FSheffield Wednesday play Sheffield
OL,14,FUnited in the Championship.
OL,16,FThe spray is a forensic tool designed
OL,17,Fto mark individuals with a uniquely
OL,18,Fcoded invisible solution that sticks
OL,19,Fto skin, clothing and personal items.
