OL,3,CPolice to use DNA tagging spray for
OL,4,Cthe first time at Sheffield derby
OL,6,FIt is detectable under UV light and is
OL,7,Ftraceable for weeks - this allows
OL,8,Fofficers to link offenders to specific
OL,9,Fincidents and locations.
OL,11,FSouth Yorkshire Police said it is
OL,12,Faware a "minority of people may look
OL,13,Fto disrupt celebrations."
OL,15,FOfficer Charlotte Bloxham said:
OL,16,F"Football should be a celebration of
OL,17,Fsport, not a platform for criminal
OL,18,Fbehaviour.
