OL,3,CPolice to use DNA tagging spray for
OL,4,Cthe first time at Sheffield derby
OL,6,F"This rollout demonstrates our
OL,7,Fproactive approach to keeping matches
OL,8,Fsafe and enjoyable for everyone.
OL,10,FThe vast majority of fans are
OL,11,Frespectful and law-abiding, and this
OL,12,Fmeasure will help us deal swiftly with
OL,13,Fthose who are not."
OL,15,FThe first Steel City derby takes place
OL,16,Fat midday on Sunday at Hillsborough
OL,17,FStadium.
